- A factory constructor can return an instance of the class or a different class. It is used for implementing design patterns like singleton. Example:

      ```dart
      class Logger {
        static final Logger _instance = Logger._internal();

        factory Logger() {
          return _instance;
        }

        Logger._internal();
      }
      ```

